            "summary": "Advent Technologies Holdings, Inc., based in Livermore, California, and listed on the NASDAQ under the ticker symbol ADN, disclosed today that it has been notified by Nasdaq on April 16, 2025, regarding non-compliance with periodic filing requirements outlined in Nasdaq Listing Rule 5250(c)(1). The basis for this notice is the delay in filing the Company\u2019s Annual Report on Form 10-K for the fiscal year ending on December 31, 2024. The report was due by March 31, 2025, and as of the notification date, it had not been submitted to the Securities and Exchange Commission.",
